Have a nice day.

00:42:24.063 --> 00:42:27.608
Level Six is furniture and home goods.
Going down.

00:42:28.776 --> 00:42:30.819
Welcome. Please watch your step.

00:42:30.903 --> 00:42:32.446
Welcome.

00:42:33.155 --> 00:42:35.074
-What the heck?
-Going down.

