You get off!

00:43:01.517 --> 00:43:03.018
That hurts.

00:43:08.691 --> 00:43:09.566
Crap…

00:43:20.369 --> 00:43:21.578
Mi-ho.

00:43:22.204 --> 00:43:23.497
What's wrong?

00:43:27.459 --> 00:43:31.130
Level Six is furniture and home goods.
Going down.

00:43:31.213 --> 00:43:32.673
Welcome.

00:43:33.257 --> 00:43:35.342
You look so cool, Mi-ho.

00:43:40.097 --> 00:43:43.726
The deputy branch manager
got so pissed I didn't have this.

00:43:45.185 --> 00:43:47.104
No one's asking for my name.

00:43:54.611 --> 00:43:56.488
The job's not bad, though.

00:43:58.115 --> 00:44:00.492
-Really?
-I get break time and a nice meal.

00:44:01.285 --> 00:44:02.327
That's a relief.

00:44:07.082 --> 00:44:10.002
And I was told I'm good at my job.

00:44:10.085 --> 00:44:12.379
I'm a candidate for employee of the month.

00:44:13.172 --> 00:44:14.298
-Really?
-Yes.

00:44:14.381 --> 00:44:16.133
Do you want anything, Beom?

00:44:17.760 --> 00:44:19.887
Wipe your mouth.

00:44:23.974 --> 00:44:24.892
Mi-ho.

00:44:25.642 --> 00:44:26.518
Yes?

00:44:29.438 --> 00:44:30.731
I'm really sorry.

00:44:30.814 --> 00:44:31.899
What for?

00:44:34.610 --> 00:44:37.821
-Did you take my clothes again?
-No.

00:44:45.621 --> 00:44:49.041
You're so good at your job
even though you're only 21 years old.

00:44:54.463 --> 00:44:55.464
So what?

00:44:58.926 --> 00:45:01.261
-I should get back to work.
-Okay.

00:45:01.345 --> 00:45:03.472
Brush your teeth when you get home.

00:45:03.555 --> 00:45:05.015
-Have a good shift.
-Okay.

00:45:30.916 --> 00:45:32.709
Yes, thank you.

00:45:32.793 --> 00:45:36.296
SMALL BUSINESS CENTER
EMERGENCY LOAN INFORMATION

00:45:45.597 --> 00:45:48.350
Hello, I'm Kang Tae-poong
from Typhoon Trading.

00:45:48.433 --> 00:45:49.476
Yes.

00:45:50.561 --> 00:45:53.855
I'm calling you about
the emergency loan for small businesses.

00:45:55.524 --> 00:45:57.901
Two months? Isn't this for emergencies?

00:45:57.985 --> 00:46:00.988
I called because it said emergency loans.

